  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Apart-Hotel Xalet Besoli is a cosy retreat offering good value for money with comfortable rooms and friendly service. Its tucked away slightly but is still within walking distance of the centre of Arinsal which offers cafes and restaurants as well as good public transport links to take you to nearby towns and villages. During the summer months, you can make use of the hotels outdoor terrace and admire the mountain views or for those cooler summer evenings head inside to the bar-café where you can enjoy a drink by the grand fire place.</p>]]></description>
